 hourse every hour to get material. <br>
<br>
If anyone want to power skill up to 400-450 range contact me. I have two 10g grants availble as of today, I will anounce more grants as I get more money. <br>
<br>
<br>
this is just my 2 cent worth. <br>
<br>
