As an added incentive, I will make the first person who gets a skill of 500 in armorcrafting and the first person who gets a skill of 500 in weaponcrafting an officer, as I already have Nimitz - our first Artisan <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   The only other requirement would be willingness to provide goods to the guild at a reasonable price! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
